<!-- All possible fields for steps are : 
* Text - Mandatory, defines the text that will be displayed
* Highlight - Optional, defines which component to highlight. Can be either a control name of fully defined class, will prioritize class.
* Circle - Optional, can be anything. Defines if a circle is to be drawn to highlight instead of a rectangle
* WaitForMessage - Optional, defines which message sent by the internal messenger the tutorial should wait for. Will remove the continue button.
* Arrow - Optional, can be anything. Defines if an arrow is to be drawn next to the highlighted control.
* RightClick - Optional, can be anything. Defines is a right click is to be sent on the highlighted control.
* CommandToRun - Optional, defines which relay command to run on the component's view model.
* MessageToSend - Optional, defines which message to send to the internal messenger.
Please request messages or control names to be added in the dev thread or on github.
-->
